line_1: And now the Wretch his destin'd End foresees,
line_2: From rankled Sores the gnawing Pains increase;

line_1: Which only a parental eye foresees,
line_2: Events improbable and strange as these,

line_1: Which only a parental eye foresees,
line_2: A public school shall bring to pass with ease.
